videos.description: South Carolina's Tyasha Harris jumps in front of the pass to get the steal and takes it down court for the easy layup.
videos.headline: Harris gets the steal and score

videos.description: South Carolina's A'ja Wilson blocks Missouri's 3-point shot attempt with seconds left on the shot clock.
videos.headline: Wilson swats away shot attempt

videos.description: Missouri's Sophie Cunningham makes the reverse layup and draws contact, Cunningham gets pumped after drawing the foul.
videos.headline: Cunningham gets pumped off the and-1

videos.description: South Carolina's A'ja Wilson puts back the missed layup attempt and draws the foul.
videos.headline: Wilson with the clutch putback

videos.description: Missouri's Sophie Cunningham grabs the offensive rebound to keep the possession and then makes the layup and draws contact.
videos.headline: Cunningham draws the and-1

videos.description: Tigers coach Robin Pingeton discusses Sophie Cunningham's 26-point game and her team's upset victory over the Gamecocks.
videos.headline: Missouri's Pingeton talks upset over No. 6 South Carolina
